task.summary: First commit. Fully working implementation for raw payments. Method of payment testing currently takes the block from start and checks each block from start to current for transactions.
Everything is updated and ready to use. The is the first alpha release of the API and should be used with that in mind.
Layout files added for CryptoTest. Web pages added as well, they should be copied to htdocs or equivalent location.
Maven dependencies updated and project as a whole cleaned up nice and fresh!
Split test project from API and cleaned up dependencies.
Added server UI to view active transactions.
Added the confirmation updates placed in the db for live tracking. Compressed startup data to all fit inside the config file.
